# ClarityDSM front-end build config.
#
# DIRECT mode (default): leave VITE_PROXY_URL unset. No Anthropic key is bundled;
# each user enters their own key in-app (stored only in their browser).
#
# PROXY mode (shared with colleagues): set VITE_PROXY_URL to your deployed proxy
# (see proxy/README.md). The proxy holds the single Anthropic key; users enter a
# shared ACCESS CODE in-app instead of a key. For GitHub Pages, set this as the
# repo Actions *variable* VITE_PROXY_URL rather than committing it here.
#
# VITE_PROXY_URL=https://your-service.onrender.com
